# Blog Content Directory

This directory contains markdown blog posts.

## File Format

Each blog post should be a `.md` or `.mdx` file with YAML frontmatter:

```markdown
---
title: "Your Post Title"
date: "2026-02-12"
description: "Brief description for SEO"
tags: ["tag1", "tag2"]
category: "development"
published: true
---

Your content here...
```

## Frontmatter Fields

| Field | Required | Description |
|-------|----------|-------------|
| title | Yes | Post title |
| date | Yes | Publication date (YYYY-MM-DD) |
| description | Yes | SEO description (160 chars max) |
| tags | No | Array of tags |
| category | No | Post category |
| published | No | Set to false to hide |
| cover | No | Cover image path |
